\begin{frame}
\frametitle{Vector Addition and Subtraction}

Addition and subtraction are element-by-element operations
\begin{align*}
    c = a + b\ \ \ &\Longleftrightarrow\ \ \ c_i = a_i + b_i\ \ \ i = 1,\ldots,n  \\
    d = a - b\ \ \ &\Longleftrightarrow\ \ \ d_i = a_i - b_i\ \ \ i = 1,\ldots,n
\end{align*}

